train

Class WaggonSeat

  • java.lang.Object
    • train.WaggonSeat

  • public class WaggonSeat
extends java.lang.Object
    A WaggonSeat is a single seat that is part of a Waggon. Each seat provides a unique seat id that is set initially when a new ticket is built. The builder attempts to reserve the specific seat and initializes the seat id with the ticket id. The SeatLocation tells on which side the seat is located inside the Waggon.
